Package structures

package structures
  • Class
    Description
    LineSchedule
    The LineSchedule class represents a line in a schedule, containing information about a particular class or event.
    Room
    The Room class represents a physical room in a building.
    RoomPreference
    The RoomPreference class hosts a series of constant values referring to ISCTE-IUL room specifications.
    RoomsTuple<ArrayList,List>
    The RoomsTuple class represents a tuple containing two elements: a list of room line data and a list of room column headers.
    ScheduleDataModel
    The ScheduleDataModel class represents the data model object associated with the scheduling application at any given time.
    ScheduleInstant
    The ScheduleInstant class represents an ISCTE-IUL time slot and date, a schedule time slot at a precise point in time.
    SchedulePeriod
    The SchedulePeriod class hosts a series of constant values referring to ISCTE-IUL schedule time slots (start and end time), time periods (periods of a day, with start and end times), and days of the week.
